GUI :
  Edit mode:
    Edit scene with keyboard
    Edit scene with mouse
    Save and load scene into the grid

Game of Life:
  Show number of generations
  Change orientation of scenes

Scene:
  A scene should be a class of its own

  Added scene shouldn't be added to the logical grid immediately,
  they should be loaded, toyed with and only logically added at the
  start of the game
  Should have a pointer on a scene that can be rotated

Bugs:
  Curses will raise exceptions when trying to create a window
  out of range of the terminal, catch error and fix the crash
